        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Though battle-hardened, none have been in a war of such a scale. A mix of nervousness and excitement quickens everyone\\'s steps.'}"
    },
    {
